NetworkPolicy
-----------------------

Configure a network policy using the frontend and backend project with the following requirements

Create a network policy named "db-allow-conn" in the "backend" project using the pod selector "network.openshift.io/policy-group", allowing
only pods from the "frontend" project (with project label "team=security" and pod label "deployment=sql" to connect on TCP port "3306",
and verify configuration by checking the logs in the frontend project.
